data.description: **PARADISE FOUND** Tucked away in the acclaimed South Fork community, this tastefully appointed and lovingly maintained four bedroom, three bathroom pool home is simply a must see! Curb appeal abounds with manicured tropical landscaping and a covered front entry welcoming you. As you step inside you’ll be greeted by an abundance of natural light and taken in by the picturesque lanai and pool views framed by the large sliding glass door found in the formal living room. The formal dining area flows nicely from the living room sharing a soaring ceiling which enhances the open and airy feeling of the home. Located just off this formal space and situated in its own private wing you’ll find an expansive owners suite with French door access directly to the lanai. The owners en-suite boasts two walk-in closets, a soaking tub, a dual sink vanity, a walk-in shower, and water closet. Open concept living shines in the great room with the kitchen overlooking both the informal dining and living areas. The kitchen is a chef’s dream with a great deal of 42” cabinetry for your storage needs, stainless steel appliances, a pantry, and island with counter height seating. Just off the kitchen is the interior laundry room with access to the attached three car garage. The great room features volume ceilings, an extended ledge for decorations, and access to the lanai through French doors. Located in the rear of the home is the guest wing which features two bedrooms sharing a jack-and-jill style bathroom and the third located next to a hall bathroom with cabana style access to the lanai and pool. Step outside into the lanai and you’ll find your own private piece of paradise! Outdoor living and dining is embraced in the covered area with an outdoor kitchen with counter height seating just steps away. The pool deck is enhanced with stone pavers and offers plenty of space to relax in the sun! The heated, saltwater pool with a cascading waterfall is just calling for you to make a splash and is easy to maintain with an in-floor cleaning system. The lanai is fully screened and the backyard fully fenced with beautiful landscaping throughout along with a nice amount of green space. The South Fork community features resort class amenities including a community pool, playground, dog park, sports courts, and miles of walking and biking trails. Wonderfully located with many shopping and dining options located just minutes away along with easy access to US 301, I-75, and the Selmon Expressway providing convenient options to downtown Tampa, MacDill AFB, Ybor City, and more! Put it all together and you’ll see why this one of a kind gem should be on the top of your list!
